<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 21 at 8:13AM EDT  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...Elevated risk of fire spread today...
Northwesterly winds gusting to 20 to 30 mph will combine with
relative humidities dropping below 30 percent in the afternoon to
produce an elevated risk of fire spread today.
Open burning is not recommended today. Follow instructions of
local fire wardens. Be careful when handling and disposing of
ignition sources outdoors, such as cigarettes or matches.</description>
